   'Judge Rowan''s adult son fell from his bedroom window to his death on the property. His grieving mother is said to roam the halls, forever searching for her lost child. The mass cholera deaths left an indelible mark on the mansion. Visitors report cold spots, unexplained sounds, and sightings of apparitions in period dress throughout the house.',
